\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Taiwan under Japanese Rule}}\n[[Category:Taiwan under Japanese rule| ]]\n[[Category:Former Japanese colonies]]\n[[Category:Former colonies in Asia]]\n[[Category:Japanese military occupations]]\n[[Category:Taiwan in World War II|*]]\n[[Category:1890s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1900s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1910s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1920s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1930s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1940s in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1895 establishments in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1895 establishments in the Japanese colonial empire]]\n[[Category:1945 disestablishments in Taiwan|*Japanese rule]]\n[[Category:1945 disestablishments in the Japanese colonial empire]]\n[[Category:1952 disestablishments in the Japanese colonial empire]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1895]]\n[[Category:States and territories disestablished in 1945]]\n[[Category:States and territories disestablished in 1952]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2015}}\n{{Short description|Period of Taiwanese history}}{{Infobox former country\n| native_name                = {{native name|zh-tw|\u65e5\u6cbb\u81fa\u7063}}<br />{{small|''Jihchih T\u02bbaiwan''}}<hr />{{native name|ja|\u5927\u65e5\u672c\u5e1d\u570b\u81fa\u7063}}<br>{{small|''Dai-Nippon Teikoku Taiwan''}}\n| conventional_long_name                = Japanese Taiwan\n| common_name                = Taiwan\n| era                = [[Empire of Japan]]\n| status                = [[Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere|Colony]] of the [[Empire of Japan]]\n| empire                = Japan\n| national_anthem                = {{ublist |\"[[Kimigayo]]\" |{{center|[[File:Kimi ga Yo 1930 instrumental.oga]]}}}}\n| government_type                = [[Government-General of Taiwan|Government-General]]\n| life_span                    = 1895-1945\n| year_start                = 1895\n| year_end                = 1952\n| event_start      